- Of course, can.

579
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:30,020
Thank you.

580
00:30:30,020 --> 00:30:30,570
You're welcome.

581
00:30:30,580 --> 00:30:31,620
I love your books.

582
00:30:31,620 --> 00:30:32,020
Thank you.

583
