592
00:30:52,740 --> 00:30:53,340
Mr. He Han.

593
00:30:55,860 --> 00:30:56,220
Handsome.

594
00:30:58,180 --> 00:30:59,580
Been here a while. Waiting for you.

595
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:02,820
