600
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,200
Let's go together.

601
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:21,580
You go ahead.

602
00:31:21,740 --> 00:31:22,711
We'll be right there.

603
00:31:25,140 --> 00:31:25,740
Mr. Gu Yan,

604
00:31:25,866 --> 00:31:27,800
