I'll take you into the hall.

605
00:31:30,660 --> 00:31:30,860
Come.

606
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:33,900
Upstairs.

607
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:36,860
Didn't Dai Shan come?

608
00:31:37,333 --> 00:31:38,444
She said she didn't want to

609
00:31:38,466 --> 00:31:40,555
