convenient for us to talk.

612
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:53,100
Mr. Fan is watching us over there.

613
00:31:53,660 --> 00:31:54,820
He's holding a contract.

614
00:31:57,940 --> 00:31:58,700
Your contract?

615
00:31:59,380 --> 00:32:00,060
Probably.

616
00:32:00,580 --> 00:32:01,220
Do well.

617
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:04,222
Mr. Zhao.

618
00:32:05,220 --> 00:32:05,700
Mr. Fan.

619
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:07,820
I thought it was two big stars,

620
00:32:08,100 --> 00:32:10,060
