624
00:32:17,380 --> 00:32:18,580
No rush, you two go ahead.

625
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:19,844
You two go ahead.

626
00:32:20,755 --> 00:32:21,860
Let's take a photo together.

627
00:32:22,020 --> 00:32:22,460
Sure.

628
00:32:22,940 --> 00:32:23,460
