629
00:32:24,060 --> 00:32:24,820
Come here.

630
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:26,540
Come.

631
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:28,460
Come.

632
00:32:28,733 --> 00:32:29,844
Alright, look over here.

633
00:32:31,444 --> 00:32:32,220
Okay, that's good.

634
00:32:33,022 --> 00:32:34,688
Make sure you get good shots of them.

635
00:32:34,777 --> 00:32:37,000
It's been a while since you
took photos together, right?

636
00:32:37,533 --> 00:32:38,620
Come, take a few more.

637
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:39,700
Look here.

638
00:32:40,700 --> 00:32:40,940
Good.

639
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:42,180
Nice.

640
00:32:42,180 --> 00:32:42,680
Mr. Gu Yan.

641
00:32:42,690 --> 00:32:43,866
Alright, don't blink, one more.

642
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:47,460
Good.

643
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,580
Don't blink. Another one.

644
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:55,620
Good.

645
00:32:56,380 --> 00:32:57,020
Look here.

646
00:32:58,780 --> 00:32:59,100
Good.

647
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:01,860
Good.

648
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:03,020
Nice, good.

649
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:04,820
Come, smile.

650
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:07,820
Good.

651
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:10,100
A bit closer.

652
00:33:10,180 --> 00:33:10,980
A little closer.

653
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,140
Nice.

654
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:13,780
You two can move closer.

655
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:14,580
Good.

656
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:15,980
Alright, maybe switch a pose.

657
00:33:16,260 --> 00:33:16,540
Good.

658
00:33:17,780 --> 00:33:18,130
Hello.

659
00:33:18,130 --> 00:33:18,660
Nice.

660
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:19,220
Hello.

661
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:20,020
Hold that.

662
00:33:20,300 --> 00:33:20,620
Good.

663
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:21,980
Good.

664
00:33:22,044 --> 00:33:22,700
Stay like that.

665
00:33:40,740 --> 00:33:41,420
Mr. He Han.

666
00:33:41,555 --> 00:33:43,210
- Hello.
- Hello, can I get your autograph?

667
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:43,980
Of course.

668
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:44,500
Come.

669
00:33:44,660 --> 00:33:45,377
Here you go.

670
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:46,460
Here.

671
00:33:46,577 --> 00:33:48,170
Mr. He Han, can I get an autograph?

672
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:48,780
Sure, sure.

673
00:33:49,020 --> 00:33:50,260
Thank you.

674
00:33:50,622 --> 00:33:51,400
Thank you.

675
00:33:51,460 --> 00:33:52,170
No problem.

676
00:33:52,170 --> 00:33:52,500
Alright.

677
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,180
- Bye.
- Bye.

678
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:54,540
Goodbye.

679
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:06,100
Mr. He Han, hello.

680
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:07,100
We're your fans.

681
00:34:07,100 --> 00:34:08,180
Could we get your autograph?

682
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:08,900
Of course.

683
00:34:09,044 --> 00:34:10,860
Lin Zhanqiao and He Han came together.

684
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:12,333
They're back together again?

685
00:34:13,088 --> 00:34:15,066
The two of them are tied together
by shared interests,

686
00:34:15,111 --> 00:34:16,850
