than an old married couple.

687
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:17,660
Mr. He, Ms. Lin,

688
00:34:17,860 --> 00:34:19,420
I really like both of you.

689
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:20,820
Can we take a photo together?

690
00:34:21,780 --> 00:34:22,580
Of course.

691
00:34:22,980 --> 00:34:23,820
Let's take it here.

692
00:34:26,266 --> 00:34:27,355
You stand in the middle.

693
00:34:34,140 --> 00:34:35,244
Your seat is over here.

694
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:47,044
Please sit.

695
00:34:53,820 --> 00:34:55,420
(Fan Shu)

696
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,300
Welcome.

697
00:34:57,620 --> 00:34:59,980
(He Han)

698
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:02,900
(Lin Zhanqiao)

699
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:03,580
Mr. Gu Yan,

700
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,460
I really love your novels.

701
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:07,066
Could we add each other on WeChat?

702
00:35:07,088 --> 00:35:07,666
Over here.

703
00:35:08,133 --> 00:35:08,666
Alright.

704
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:09,300
Thank you.

705
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,266
I'll scan you.

706
00:35:12,133 --> 00:35:13,090
- Please have a seat.
- Sent.

707
00:35:13,090 --> 00:35:13,533
Thank you.

708
00:35:13,622 --> 00:35:14,540
I really enjoy your work.

709
00:35:14,540 --> 00:35:15,820
Looking forward to more.

710
00:35:16,340 --> 00:35:17,044
Thank you.

711
00:35:18,911 --> 00:35:19,980
That over there is Gu Yan.

712
00:35:20,100 --> 00:35:20,820
I'll go say hello.

713
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:21,700
Sure.

714
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,900
Got his WeChat.

715
00:35:27,180 --> 00:35:27,580
Gu Yan.

716
00:35:29,133 --> 00:35:29,888
I'm Zhao Lanxin.

717
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:30,980
We've met before.

718
00:35:32,060 --> 00:35:32,540
Hello.

719
00:35:33,600 --> 00:35:35,700
I've been wanting to
find a chance to talk to you,

720
00:35:35,900 --> 00:35:37,620
but Lin Zhanqiao
kept you too well hidden.

721
00:35:37,740 --> 00:35:39,088
I couldn't find the opportunity.

722
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:40,380
I...

723
00:35:40,940 --> 00:35:42,300
I've signed

724
00:35:42,333 --> 00:35:44,511
a long-term exclusive
contract with Lin Zhanqiao.

725
00:35:44,533 --> 00:35:45,900
I can't have any form of cooperation

726
00:35:45,900 --> 00:35:47,140
with other companies anymore.

727
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:49,111
That doesn't stop me
from liking your novels.

728
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:50,260
In my view,

729
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:51,900
you're more talented than He Han,

730
00:35:52,060 --> 00:35:53,644
and your character is better, too.

731
00:35:53,666 --> 00:35:55,300
If Lin Zhanqiao doesn't elevate you

732
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:56,260
to his level,

733
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:57,980
that's unfair to you.

734
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:00,820
I'm still a newcomer.

735
00:36:00,955 --> 00:36:02,260
I haven't thought that far ahead.

736
00:36:02,260 --> 00:36:03,540
Fame should come early.

737
00:36:04,022 --> 00:36:05,444
If you don't fight for it yourself,

738
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:06,780
someone like He Han

739
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:08,180
won't step aside for you.

740
00:36:09,200 --> 00:36:11,022
Come, let's add each other on WeChat.

741
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:18,260
That's definitely fine.

742
00:36:20,866 --> 00:36:22,288
Mr. Fan, I'll head over first.

743
00:36:25,260 --> 00:36:25,540
Come.

744
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:28,460
Lanxin.

745
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:29,820
Mr. Fan.

746
00:36:29,900 --> 00:36:30,900
When did you get here?

747
00:36:30,955 --> 00:36:31,911
I didn't even notice.

748
00:36:32,620 --> 00:36:33,300
You're busy.

749
00:36:33,380 --> 00:36:34,290
But I saw you.

750
00:36:34,290 --> 00:36:35,500
You came in with Lin Zhanqiao.

751
00:36:35,780 --> 00:36:36,500
Come, have a seat.

752
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,222
Alright.

753
00:36:43,580 --> 00:36:45,300
I was worried you might not come.

754
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:47,280
It's nothing.
Just something at the branch office.

755
00:36:49,540 --> 00:36:50,450
This way, please.

756
00:36:50,450 --> 00:36:51,460
If I remember correctly,

757
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,980
you missed last year's

758
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:53,980
Author Night, right?

759
00:36:54,466 --> 00:36:55,780
Yes, I was on a business trip.

760
00:36:57,500 --> 00:36:59,140
Look, He Han and Lin Zhanqiao are here.

761
00:36:59,380 --> 00:37:00,700
What a perfect pair.

762
00:37:04,977 --> 00:37:06,860
The data for
Shattered Six States this year

763
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:07,740
has been impressive.

764
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:22,660
Why is Gu Yan sitting over there?

765
00:37:25,111 --> 00:37:27,444
Mr. Fan probably wants to
take care of the newcomer.

766
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:32,620
Dear guests,

767
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:34,300
respected authors,

768
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:35,660
ladies and gentlemen,

769
00:37:36,140 --> 00:37:37,900
good evening.

770
00:37:40,620 --> 00:37:42,620
(Welcome to Dingqi Reading Platform)

771
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:44,740
(2024 Annual Author Night.)

772
00:37:45,140 --> 00:37:46,540
(I am your host, Ji Xinjie.)

773
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:49,820
(It is a great honor to spend
this evening with all of you,)

774
00:37:50,020 --> 00:37:51,460
(filled with literary charm)

775
00:37:51,580 --> 00:37:53,140
(and sparks of creativity.)

776
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,711
Over the past year,

777
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:56,500
Dingqi's creative
energy has been thriving.

778
00:37:56,860 --> 00:37:58,980
A new generation of
authors has risen strongly,

779
00:37:59,088 --> 00:38:00,900
with hit works
emerging one after another.

780
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:02,700
In expanding overseas,

781
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:05,220
we have moved forward steadily
to new heights.

782
00:38:05,311 --> 00:38:06,940
In intellectual property adaptations,

783
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:09,488
we have continued to deepen our efforts
and make breakthroughs.

784
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:12,540
Dingqi has always been committed
to supporting its authors

785
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:14,820
so that great works
can reach more people

786
00:38:14,980 --> 00:38:16,420
and create greater value.

787
00:38:16,940 --> 00:38:18,820
Next, let us welcome with applause

788
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:20,940
the Head of Dingqi Content Department,

789
00:38:21,180 --> 00:38:22,900
Mr. Fan Shu, to deliver a speech.

790
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,044
Please welcome him.

791
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:38,711
(Thank you, everyone.)

792
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:43,380
(Thank you to all
our outstanding authors.)

793
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:45,020
Because of your hard work,

794
00:38:45,620 --> 00:38:46,820
over the past year,

795
00:38:47,380 --> 00:38:49,900
Dingqi has achieved remarkable results.

796
00:38:50,740 --> 00:38:52,660
That's why we can have

797
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:54,820
such a star-filled evening today.

798
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:56,980
The first major award

799
00:38:57,180 --> 00:38:58,820
we are about to present

800
00:38:59,660 --> 00:39:02,620
is the New Rising Author of the Year.

801
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:05,060
I'd like to invite a presenter

802
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:07,060
to reveal

803
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:08,580
and present this award.

804
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:10,460
This guest

805
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:13,700
is widely recognized in the industry

806
00:39:14,180 --> 00:39:15,300
as one of the most talented

807
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:18,980
and influential authors.

808
00:39:19,580 --> 00:39:20,220
He is also

809
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:22,740
the brightest star

810
00:39:23,780 --> 00:39:25,020
of tonight's Author Night.

811
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,355
Please welcome He Han.

812
00:40:00,222 --> 00:40:01,140
Thank you, everyone.

813
00:40:01,340 --> 00:40:02,540
Thank you, Dingqi Platform,

814
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:04,620
and thank you to our dear readers.

815
00:40:04,860 --> 00:40:06,460
Without you, there would be no us.

816
00:40:07,340 --> 00:40:10,660
This is my fourth time
attending Author Night,

817
00:40:10,977 --> 00:40:12,266
and it's a great honor.

818
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:14,740
The award I'm about to present today

819
00:40:14,740 --> 00:40:17,180
is also very meaningful to me,

820
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:20,580
because when I received
this award back then,

821
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:22,820
the person who stood by my side

822
00:40:23,140 --> 00:40:24,260
was my great partner,

823
00:40:24,740 --> 00:40:25,380
Lin Zhanqiao.

824
00:40:26,333 --> 00:40:28,500
Although I'm not here to
receive an award this year,

825
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:30,300
the person beside me

826
00:40:30,740 --> 00:40:31,460
is still her.

827
00:40:36,460 --> 00:40:38,940
In an ever-changing industry like ours,

828
00:40:39,311 --> 00:40:41,100
the most important thing,
what we need most,

829
00:40:41,620 --> 00:40:43,460
is exactly this kind of

830
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:45,140
mutual trust and lasting partnership.

831
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:47,900
On the path of creation,

832
00:40:48,060 --> 00:40:48,860
Lin Zhanqiao and I

833
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:50,888
could be described
as growing up together.

834
00:40:58,700 --> 00:41:00,900
(The 8th Dingqi
Literary Influence Ranking)

835
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:03,020
Although recently, we've each begun

836
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:05,540
new attempts and explorations,

837
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:07,260
I've always believed

838
00:41:07,740 --> 00:41:08,820
that a temporary parting

839
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:10,860
is for a better reunion.

840
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:17,940
Here, I also want to wish

841
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:19,660
all the young creators

842
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:21,540
that you can be

843
00:41:21,540 --> 00:41:22,555
as fortunate as I was

844
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:23,820
to meet an editor

845
00:41:24,100 --> 00:41:26,340
who truly understands you
from the very beginning.

846
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:29,140
And I hope you learn from me,

847
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:31,060
