848
00:41:31,140 --> 00:41:32,100
and cherish

849
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:34,940
the partner who stands
by you and supports you.

850
00:41:46,444 --> 00:41:47,911
Alright, without further ado,

851
00:41:48,100 --> 00:41:50,580
