852
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:52,340
New Rising Author Award.

853
00:41:53,380 --> 00:41:54,422
The winner is

854
00:41:55,700 --> 00:41:56,300
Gu Yan.

855
00:42:06,620 --> 00:42:07,420
He's not here?

856
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,540
Please understand.

857
00:42:09,140 --> 00:42:10,580
The young man might be a bit nervous,

858
00:42:10,580 --> 00:42:12,260
so he stepped out to gather himself.

859
00:42:13,460 --> 00:42:15,260
I'll accept it on his behalf.

860
00:42:15,933 --> 00:42:16,770
Thank you, everyone.

861
00:42:16,780 --> 00:42:17,500
(Gu Yan)

862
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:18,940
(Drunk Old Friend)

863
00:42:50,100 --> 00:42:50,580
Zhanqiao,

864
00:42:51,980 --> 00:42:52,460
let's talk.

865
00:42:56,180 --> 00:42:56,620
Let's talk?

866
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

867
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

868
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

869
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

